casebody.data:
FLORIDA, plaintiff,
v.
GEORGIA. No. 142, Original. Supreme Court of the United States March 20, 2017. The Report of the Special Master is received and ordered filed. Exceptions to the Report, with supporting briefs, may be filed within 45 days. Replies, if any, with supporting briefs, may filed within 30 days. Sur-replies, if any, with supporting briefs, may be filed within 30 days.
